com.xuggle.xuggler.io
Interface IURLProtocolRegistrar

public interface IURLProtocolRegistrar

For Internal Use Only. A signature interface for objects that want to register protocols for Xuggler to use.

Method Summary
 void registerProtocol(String protocol, URLProtocolManager manager)
          Tells Xuggler that any requests for a given protocol should be redirected to the given manager.
 

Method Detail

registerProtocol

void registerProtocol(String protocol,
                      URLProtocolManager manager)
Tells Xuggler that any requests for a given protocol should be redirected to the given manager.

NOTE: Protocol can only be alpha-characters; no numbers or punctuation.

Parameters:
protocol - The protocol (alpha-only) without ":"
manager - The manager object you want to use.
